name: Ethnicity
definition: category based on a cultural factors, including nationality, regional culture, ancestry, and language
label: ethnicity

name: HMDA-Report
label: HMDA report
definition: a report prepared to satisfy HMDA regulatory reporting requirements as described US section 1003.3(c) of the Revised Home Mortgage Disclosure Act of 2015

name: UniversalLoanIdentifier
label: universal loan identifier
explanatoryNote: In the US, the structure of this identifier is defined in the 2015 revision to the Home Mortgage Disclosure Act.
definition: unique identifier given to unequivocally identify a specific loan secured by real estate

name: HMDA-Disposition
label: HMDA disposition
definition: a type of action taken regarding an application for a HMDA covered loan

name: HMDA-CoveredLoanContract
label: HMDA covered loan contract
definition: a closed-end mortgage loan or open-end line of credit that is not an excluded transaction for HMDA reporting under US section 1003.3(c) of the Revised Home Mortgage Disclosure Act of 2015

name: Race
label: race
definition: a category based on a person's physical characteristics, such as bone structure and skin, hair, or eye color

name: HowSubmitted
definition: category indicating whether the applicant or borrower submitted the application for the covered loan directly to the reporting financial institution
label: how submitted

name: HMDA-PreApprovalRequest
definition: a request for pre-approval of a home purchase loan up to a certain amount, and subject to certain non-credit related conditions
explanatoryNote: This request is approved only after a comprehensive analysis of the credit worthiness of the borrower is carried out.
label: HMDA pre-approval request

name: ConstructionType_MobileHome
explanatoryNote: It does not meet HUD code.
definition: a dwelling unit constructed on a base frame which features wheels and axles to be used in transporting home from place to place
label: mobile home

name: ConstructionType_Modular
label: modular
definition: a factory-built dwelling not on a permanent chassis

name: ConstructionType_OnFrameModular
label: on frame modular
definition: a factory built dwelling on a permanent chassis which does not have a HUD label

name: ConstructionType_Manufactured
definition: a factory-built dwelling built in compliance with the Federal Manufactured Home Construction and Safety Standards in effect at the time the home was manufactured as evidenced by the HUD label
label: manufactured

name: ConstructionType_SiteBuilt
definition: describes construction process, indicating that most elements are created at the homes permanent site. May include some prefabricated components
label: site built

name: hasHMDA-DispositionDate
definition: the date associated with the HMDA Disposition for a HMDA Covered Loan
label: HMDA disposition date
